object.script:
function dl(ax,ay,bx,by) screen.drawLine(ax,ay,bx,by) end
function gb(n) return input.getBool(n) end
function gn(n) return input.getNumber(n) end
function onTick() mag=gb(2) at_shell_ready=gb(31) at_loaded=gb(32) rangefinder=gn(32) end
colw=5 rowh=6
function onDraw()
local magstr local crossgap=1 local crossleg=4
w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() cx=w/2 cy=h/2
-- Crosshair screen.setColor(0,255,0) dl(cx,cy-crossgap,cx,cy-crossgap-crossleg) dl(cx,cy+crossgap,cx,cy+crossgap+crossleg) dl(cx-crossgap-crossleg,cy,cx-crossgap,cy) dl(cx+crossgap+crossleg,cy,cx+crossgap,cy)
-- Rangefinder screen.drawText(cx+crossgap+crossleg+colw,cy,string.format("%.0fm",rangefinder))
-- Magazine indicator if mag then magstr="L" else magstr="R" end screen.drawText(w-colw*5,h-rowh,"MAG " .. magstr)
-- Main cannon chamber indiator if not at_loaded then if at_shell_ready then screen.setColor(255,255,0) else screen.setColor(255,0,0) end end screen.drawText(0,h-rowh, "MAIN CAN") end

node.label: Current gear in
node.description: Gear shift number

object.script:
function gn(x) return input.getNumber(x) end
function gb(x) return input.getBool(x) end
function onTick() clutch=gb(1) bat=gn(2) temp=gn(3) speed=gn(5) rpm=gn(6) gear=gn(7) end
colw=5 rowh=6
function gear_name(x) if x==0 then return "N" elseif x==-1 then return "R" else return string.format("%.0f",x) end end
function rg(bool) local c={0,255}
if bool then c[1]=255 c[2]=0 end screen.setColor(c[1],c[2],0) end
function onDraw()
local str
w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight()
str=string.format("%5.0f KPH\n%5.0f RPM", speed, rpm) screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,0,w,rowh,str)
rg(temp>95) screen.drawTextBox(0,rowh*2,w,rowh,string.format("%3.2f C",temp))
rg(bat<25) screen.drawTextBox(0,rowh*3,w,rowh,string.format("%3.2f BAT",bat))
screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawTextBox(0,rowh*4,w,rowh,string.format("GEAR %s",gear_name(gear)))
if clutch then screen.setColor(255,0,0) end screen.drawTextBox(colw*7,rowh*4,w,rowh,"CLUTCH")
end

object.script:
function gn(x) return input.getNumber(x) end
function gb(x) return input.getBool(x) end
function onTick() gear=gn(1) clutch=gb(1) end
function onDraw() local gear_name w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() cx=w/2 cy=h/2
if clutch then screen.setColor(64,0,0) screen.drawText(0,0,"Clutch") end
if gear == -1 then gear_name="R" elseif gear == 0 then gear_name="N" else gear_name=string.format("%x",gear) end
screen.setColor(0,255,0) screen.drawTextBox(cx,cy, 5, 5, gear_name) end
